metadata.name: Oddity #1
metadata.description:
CATHEDRAL (2014)
Cave system in the Lake District, United Kingdom.

A self-diagnosis, in search of trinkets.

'Unremarkable Oddities' is a snapshot of inner tension between spectator-ship inaction and active acknowledgement. It is the discovery that never was, the double takes unnoticed, and the manifestations from the back of your mind.

4000x3200 jpeg

Primary and all subsequent secondary owners are entitled to a 4R print of the photograph, numbered and signed on the back by the photographer.
